1
00:00:08,083 --> 00:00:10,416
[clock ticking]

2
00:00:10,500 --> 00:00:13,375
[KODAI] It's impossible
to resist causality.

3
00:00:13,458 --> 00:00:15,833
This is the correction of chaos.

4
00:00:17,708 --> 00:00:20,250
It seems that you weren't meant
to be in that world after all,

5
00:00:20,333 --> 00:00:22,083
so a correction must be made.

6
00:00:22,166 --> 00:00:25,791
You will be sent back
to where it all began.

7
00:00:25,875 --> 00:00:28,541
[TAKUYA]
Wait, what are you saying?

8
00:00:28,625 --> 00:00:30,416
It's fairly simple, really.

9
00:00:30,500 --> 00:00:33,125
You'll experience the same
events over again.

10
00:00:33,208 --> 00:00:35,291
Only this time everything
is going to play out

11
00:00:35,375 --> 00:00:37,375
slightly different than before.

12
00:00:39,500 --> 00:00:41,791
Takuya, remember this:

13
00:00:41,875 --> 00:00:45,125
Causality rules over
everything in this world.

14
00:00:45,208 --> 00:00:49,458
To discover its vast and deep
secrets is to explore history.

15
00:00:49,541 --> 00:00:51,166
[TAKUYA]
What does that mean, though?

16
00:00:51,250 --> 00:00:53,083
Hey! Dad!

17
00:00:53,166 --> 00:00:56,083
Answer me! Answer me!

18
00:00:56,166 --> 00:00:58,916
[clock ticking]

19
00:01:02,125 --> 00:01:04,333
[TAKUYA grunting]

20
00:01:06,916 --> 00:01:08,375
Mount Sankaku?

21
00:01:08,458 --> 00:01:10,333
So I'm re-starting from here?

22
00:01:10,416 --> 00:01:12,625
[TAKUYA groaning]

23
00:01:16,791 --> 00:01:20,041
[TAKUYA] It's gonna suck if
I have to keep doing this.

24
00:02:52,041 --> 00:02:55,125
[phone ringing]

25
00:02:55,208 --> 00:02:56,416
Uh?

26
00:02:58,541 --> 00:02:59,666
Hello?

27
00:02:59,750 --> 00:03:01,750
[YUKI] This is your
friendly wake-up call!

28
00:03:01,833 --> 00:03:04,958
From the one who's here in your
hour of need, hero on call,

29
00:03:05,041 --> 00:03:06,666
Masakatsu Yuki!

30
00:03:06,750 --> 00:03:08,875
[TAKUYA] Dude, where do
you get all this energy?

31
00:03:08,958 --> 00:03:11,916
Did somebody wake up on the
wrong side of the bed today?

32
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:15,125
