start tomorrow.

34
00:03:17,875 --> 00:03:19,041
[YUKI]
Could you not sleep?

35
00:03:19,125 --> 00:03:22,291
You did get a good nap
in class yesterday.

36
00:03:22,375 --> 00:03:24,541
[TAKUYA] Actually. I saw
a pretty terrible monster,

37
00:03:24,625 --> 00:03:26,250
