56
00:04:17,791 --> 00:04:19,416
Oh, stop it, you're so silly.

57
00:04:19,500 --> 00:04:21,875
[RYUZOJI, AYUMI laughing]

58
00:04:21,958 --> 00:04:24,250
[AYUMI]
Oh, Takuya!

59
00:04:24,333 --> 00:04:25,791
[door closes]

60
00:04:25,875 --> 00:04:29,250
[TAKUYA] Hey. Didn't you two
see each other just last night?

61
