about this. So, thank you.

140
00:07:57,291 --> 00:08:00,333
Please. Let me know if
you find anything.

141
00:08:01,458 --> 00:08:03,708
[TAKUYA, YUKI sputtering]

142
00:08:03,791 --> 00:08:06,458
[YUKI] I can do this,
I can do this, I can do it,

143
00:08:06,541 --> 00:08:08,583
almost done, ha, ha, ha!

144
00:08:08,666 --> 00:08:11,583
[TAKUYA, YUKI]
We're done!

145
00:08:11,666 --> 00:08:14,125
[ERIKO] Once you turn
those in, you can go.

146
00:08:14,208 --> 00:08:15,500
[BOTH]
All right!

147
00:08:15,583 --> 00:08:17,416
[BOTH laughing]

148
00:08:17,500 --> 00:08:19,041
[YUKI]
Huh? You really have to go

149
00:08:19,125 --> 00:08:21,166
to Ryuzoji's house
right now, Boss?

150
00:08:21,250 --> 00:08:23,833
'Fraid so, I'm takin'
him my dad's stuff.

151
00:08:23,916 --> 00:08:25,541
[YUKI] Well, You're
a lot braver than I am.

152
00:08:25,625 --> 00:08:28,208
That mansion of his
totally creeps me out.

153
00:08:28,291 --> 00:08:29,750
You coward.

154
00:08:29,833 --> 00:08:31,041
I want to go, too!

155
00:08:31,125 --> 00:08:32,916
I mean, it's only fair
since he promised me

156
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:35,666
before that I would
get to see his tapestry.

157
00:08:35,750 --> 00:08:37,875
[TAKUYA] Look, I'm just
going to take some stuff,

158
00:08:37,958 --> 00:08:40,291
and this one's all
I need to carry it.

159
00:08:40,375 --> 00:08:42,875
Wait, did you say
I'm going with you?

160
00:08:42,958 --> 00:08:45,416
[MIO] It would be awkward
for me to visit him on my own.

161
00:08:45,500 --> 00:08:47,833
So, this is a good
chance for me to go!

162
00:08:47,916 --> 00:08:51,750
Well, I don't mind you coming if
you feel that strongly about it.

163
00:08:51,833 --> 00:08:52,583
[TAKUYA, MIO, YUKI gasp]

164
00:08:52,666 --> 00:08:54,125
You wanna come, too?

165
00:08:54,208 --> 00:08:56,041
I need to head home now.

166
00:08:56,125 --> 00:08:58,500
[TAKUYA] Aren't you at all
curious about Ryuzoji's house?

167
00:08:58,583 --> 00:09:01,333
Everyone's talking about
it 'cause of the curse.

168
00:09:01,416 --> 00:09:04,333
He smells different.
Different from everyone else.

169
00:09:04,416 --> 00:09:06,708
[BOTH]
Uh?

170
00:09:06,791 --> 00:09:09,875
Ryuzoji is not the same.

171
00:09:11,083 --> 00:09:12,333
[TAKUYA, MIO]
Uh...

172
00:09:22,583 --> 00:09:25,500
Hatano can be kind of
tough to talk to, huh?

173
00:09:25,583 --> 00:09:28,833
She's pretty intense,
it's true. So hot.

174
00:09:28,916 --> 00:09:31,791
She seems to be avoiding
people deliberately.

175
00:09:31,875 --> 00:09:34,166
But yeah, she's hot!

176
00:09:34,250 --> 00:09:36,416
[BOYS]
Like, really, really hot.

177
00:09:36,500 --> 00:09:40,250
Wow, what a shock that the boys
are into the mysterious beauty.

178
00:09:44,125 --> 00:09:47,416
[doorbell buzzes]

179
00:09:48,500 --> 00:09:51,458
I stand by it.
This place is terrifying.

180
00:09:51,541 --> 00:09:52,708
[door creaks]

181
00:09:56,625 --> 00:09:58,041
Well, hello, young people,

182
00:09:58,125 --> 00:10:00,708
